snippet.textDisplay:
Waking up in the fall: a cup of coffee in hand, the fresh breeze of a new dawn, and the leaves of the trees colored orange and red, symbolizing autumn. A quiet morning and a good breakfast, what a fantastic way to start the day! Every step on the leaves, fallen from the trees, recalls the days of childhood. After such a hot summer, we need this autumnal calm, this cool breeze, the view of a twilight gilded by the leaves and the setting sun. May God bless you this fall, my good friend.
